<plot>Stay With Me is the dramatic story of Soda, a loner who comes from a broken home. Seeking acceptance by her peers she befriends Roman. A guy who has big dreams of life, which never amount to anything more than dreams. Soda's life begins sinking into the darkness of addiction with Roman along her side, completely oblivious. As an overdose takes control of Soda, she questions her actions and morals, and makes a decision that will greatly impact the rest of her life and Romans.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?514719</url></doc>
